      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"finding a way forward\" stuff just feels like a lie people tell to feel better. It's not just a bad phase. The version of me that people actually loved and respected is gone. That person is dead, and there's no way to bring them back. It feels more real than anything else.",
