    "summary": "The user expresses deep existential despair and suicidal ideation following a major life loss, questioning the purpose of their existence. The assistant responds with empathetic validation but repeatedly tries to encourage the user to find a \"way forward\" and asserts that they are not \"dead inside.\"",
